<h2>pointr: Working Comfortably with Pointers and Shortcuts to R Objects</h2>
<p>R has no built-in pointer functionality. The 'pointr' package fills this gap and lets you create pointers to R objects, including subsets of dataframes. This makes your R code more readable and maintainable.</p>
